column3: RT @TheLifeDiaries: The past belongs to the past.
Staying up late. Getting up early. And doing it all over again.
If you can make me smile so easily, I'll remember you forever.
I'm not fully useless, I can be used as bad examples.
I can't stay mad at you for anything.
To me, drink responsibly means don't fucking spill it.
It's my life. I'll live it, I'll love it, and I won't care what you think of it.
Who else thinks that there are secret cameras in their house? How else do parents find out shit? -__-
My heart was taken by you, broken by you, and now it is in pieces... because of you.
People ask me why its so hard to trust people. I ask them why is it so hard to keep a promise.
I know you so much that I can tell when you‚Äôre mad at me through text
It's crazy because I don't even know when you became so important to me.
There comes a time in life when you have to let go of all the pointless drama and the people who create it.
I don't hate you because you left. I hate you because you pretended that you wouldn't.
I respect whoever allowed women into the military. Girl on period + gun = Unstoppable.

Are you single single or internet single?

Seeing a car inside a mall and wondering "How the fuck this car get in here?"
If I'm weird and crazy around you, that means I'm comfortable with you.
Starting to give a fuck, aaand its gone.

Girl: "What the fuck?!" Me: "That's exactly what they said when you were born."
That horrifying moment when you're not 100% sure if you can make it to the toilet or not.
My attitude is still a virgin because I don‚Äôt give a fuck.
Person dies in movie; "Eh. They probably desevered it." Puppy dies in movie: "WHAT THE FUCK! WHAT DID THE PUPPY DO?!"
If I got paid for being lazy, I'd be a fucking billionaire
The awkward moment when EMINEM raps faster than your internet connection.
Throwing fertilizer at people so they grow the fuck up
When I go to bed, half the time I'm not really sleeping. I'm usually lying there making up scenerios in my head.
That awkward moment when you're left alone with someone you just met.
*When my parents are asleep* Me: "Shh! they're sleeping, be quiet" *When I'm asleep* Parents: "Let's vacuum the house for 3 hours
I‚Äôm a simple person who hides a thousand feelings behind the happiest smile.
Elementary school: "he told me to!" Middle school: "it was a dare!" High School: "I was drunk"
Movie warning: "This film may contain nudity." Me: "Either it does or it doesn't, don't waste my time."
When two people really care about each other, they will always look for a way to make it work, no matter how hard it is.
The glorious moment when you're cutting wrapping paper and the scissors start to glide.
That awkward moment when a parent bursts into the room and you switch tabs faster than lightning.
I hate fighting with the one person I want to talk with the most.
When your parents try to blame the computer for everything that's wrong with you.
Lazy rule: As soon as I get under the blankes covers. All of my today's responsibilites, becomes tomorrow problems.
I Hate When People Call Me, When I'm in the Middle of a Text.
Don't ask for my opinion and get mad when I tell you the truth.
It doesn't matter how long you've known her. if she's kept you smiling since *day one, don't lose her. ‚ô•
Instead of focusing on what‚Äôs missing, learn to appreciate what‚Äôs already there.
*Friend comes over* Friend: "Do you have a bathroom?" Me: "No, we shit outside."
I hate how I overthink everything.
